sequenceDiagram
    participant RT as Workflow Runtime
    participant JS as 演化腳本
    participant RA as read-state agent
    participant BA as build agent
    participant WA as write-state agent
    RT->>JS: 啟動 args v2 statePath spec
    Note over JS: args 字串先 JSON.parse
    JS->>JS: Phase Append 開始
    JS->>RA: 派 haiku 用 Read 讀 feature_list.json
    RA-->>JS: 回 features JSON（v1 留下 2 個）
    Note over JS: 算 existingNames locked baseId<br/>APPEND diff 出 1 個新 Q&A
    JS->>JS: Phase Build 開始
    par 只對新功能派 builder
        JS->>BA: 建 Q&A 功能 禁工具
        BA-->>JS: name passes:true note
    end
    Note over JS: 鎖 2 個 stable<br/>用 index 合併新舊
    JS->>JS: Phase Persist 開始
    JS->>WA: 把 merged JSON 覆寫回 state 檔
    WA-->>JS: written:true count 3
    JS-->>RT: 回 locked_stable 2 appended 1
    Note over RT: v2 共 3 agent 362k token 34s
